text: Stuff Ltd (formerly Fairfax New Zealand) is a private news media corporation in New Zealand. It owns Stuff, the country`s biggest news website, and operate nine day by day newspapers,including The Dominion Post and The Press the New Zealand's second and third-highest circulation daily newspapers, and the best weekly publication, Sunday Star-Times. Stuff additionally owns social media community Neighbourly. == References == Category:Printing Category:Newspapers published in New Zealand
